FBIS4-10160 "drlat068_g_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-068 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 Guatemala Congress Views Attacks on Deputies Congress Views Attacks on Deputies Session Held on Attacks PA0704221094 Guatemala City Teleonce Television in Spanish 1900 GMT 7 Apr 94 PA0704221094 Guatemala City Teleonce Television Spanish BFN [From the "Teleprensa" newscast] [Text] The National Congress has declared itself in permanent session to discuss the actions against members of this institutions, including the attack against Deputy Obdulio Chinchilla Vega, the attempted kidnapping of Deputy Rene Barrios Samayoa, and threats against Deputy Jose Lobo Dubon. The deputies are analyzing the possibility of asking the United Nations to immediately appoint a special rapporteur to Guatemala.
